{
  "stem": "17299.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 237.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my other brother, Bruno, he got a-- had an argument with an SS-- member of the SS-- and he got accused of so-called Rassenschande, and he had to leave Germany illegally in 1936.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he had to go over the border by the night not to be arrested by the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he went to Chile.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Santiago Chile.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rassenschande, even though he had no date with a German girl.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some farmers who owed my father money would not pay up anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even if you would take them to court, the court was against the Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say after '35 when the Nuremberg Laws went in effect.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the first time we saw in 1933 when the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then we had two members of the Nazi party standing in front of our house that nobody should go in and out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was in 1933 and April 1.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After that, we didn't hear or see anything till 1935.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we openly got insulted as dirty Jews and things like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you could not go in a bar anymore later on and things like that, but otherwise, there were no prohibitions.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not at that time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not in '35.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On a street nearby, and we didn't hear and see much of them, but when they marched with the-- through the streets and like that, the Jews made sure they were not on the streets and they were in the houses.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we heard rumors about concentration camps, and we know that some Gentiles were arrested, too.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Were communists and things like that, that they went on trial and went to jail, and things like that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We heard about that, and also that some Jews got killed in the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
